{"id":312363,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/【麻辣总局】邝飚｜敢于亮剑/","date":"2013-09-06T21:41:18Z","modified":"2013-09-07T04:37:48Z","title":"【麻辣总局】邝飚：“敢于亮剑”","content":"<p>来源：新浪微博 <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/bbc-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%96%97%E4%BA%89%E4%BD%A0%E6%AD%BB%E6%88%91%E6%B4%BB/\">@漫画局</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/亮剑.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-312365\" alt=\"亮剑\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/亮剑.jpg\" width=\"574\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/亮剑.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/09/亮剑-300x209.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@漫画局：【剑人亮剑】要你三务公开“亮相”，你偏要“亮剑”；要你官员财产“亮兜”，你偏要“亮剑”；——果真是要你学刀，你偏要学剑；要你学上剑，你偏要学下剑；金剑你不要，偏偏要银剑；放着剑客、剑侠、剑仙你不当，偏要当剑人</p>\n<p>背景新闻：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/bbc-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%84%8F%E8%AF%86%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E6%96%97%E4%BA%89%E4%BD%A0%E6%AD%BB%E6%88%91%E6%B4%BB/\">中国官媒重提意识形态斗争“你死我活”</a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[19215,19665]}